<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Ticket Assigned</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #334155;
        }

        /* Main container */
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }

        /* Header section with gradient */
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .success-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .success-icon img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .header-title {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header-subtitle {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Content section */
        .email-content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .ticket-info {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .ticket-detail {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .ticket-detail:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .detail-label {
            color: #64748b;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .detail-value {
            color: #334155;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* CTA Button */
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #2563eb;
        }

        /* Footer section */
        .email-footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .footer-links {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .footer-text {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                margin: 20px;
                border-radius: 12px;
            }

            .email-header {
                padding: 30px 15px;
            }

            .email-content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .success-icon {
                width: 300px;
                height: 300px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="email-header">
            <div class="success-icon">
                <img src="https://e7.pngegg.com/pngimages/511/969/png-clipart-red-and-black-rocket-illustration-rocket-spacecraft-rocket-image-file-formats-cartoon.png" alt="New Ticket Icon">
            </div>
            <h1 class="header-title">New Ticket Assigned</h1>
            <p class="header-subtitle">A new  ticket requires your attention</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Section -->
        <div class="email-content">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= employeeName %></strong>,</p>
            
            <div class="ticket-info  font-weight: bolder; ">
                <div class="ticket-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Ticket ID : </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">#<%= ticketId %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="ticket-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Assignment Date : </span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="ticket-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Priority : </span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= priority || 'Normal' %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>A new support ticket has been assigned to you. Please review and take the necessary action as soon as possible.</p>

            <p>If you need any assistance or have questions about this assignment, please don't hesitate to contact your supervisor or the IT team.</p>

            <a  class="cta-button">Login to dashboard to View Ticket Details</a>

            <p>Best regards,<br>TicketFlow Support Team</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <div class="email-footer">
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a class="footer-link">Help Center</a>
                <a  class="footer-link">Contact Us</a>
                <a class="footer-link">Feedback</a>
            </div>
            <p class="footer-text">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TicketFlow. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>